{"tid":243253,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國：中國正在建造兩艘098核潛艇　電磁推進0噪音　　","createTime":"2017-05-14T13:43:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-15T05:37:10.000Z","uid":58099,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0de5cdf5bf3d02d7b3420f88c00642b988a38543","tid":243253,"uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T13:43:13.000Z","msg":"美國衛星近日檢測到中國正在建造兩艘配備12套發射裝置、裝備彈道導彈的新型核潛艇。有報導猜測，兩艘核潛艇正是解放軍研制的第四代098戰略核潛艇。<br />\n<br />\n098電磁推進核潛艇。它的原理就是利用電磁力推進裝置做動力，取代傳統的螺旋槳，這使潛艇在航行的時候不會發出任何的噪音，能瞬間爆發出強大的馬力，使得核潛艇能達到100節最高航速，快於普通高速魚雷。<br />\n<br />\n報導指，到2025年之前，中國海軍會部署3-4個航母戰鬥群。屆時，第四代戰略核潛艇將成為中國潛艇部隊的主力。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://upload.lsforum.net/users/public/a628456353g63.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fupload.lsforum.net%2Fusers%2Fpublic%2Fa628456353g63.jpg&h=bdf5e11e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fa296c2e6985775e680ec8e853bf50c9ccdd09c0","tid":243253,"uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T13:52:06.000Z","msg":","},{"pid":"7b2f1c9b05ef8ec764da18f9ed5a5a338d8a6bf6","tid":243253,"uid":2590,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T13:54:03.000Z","msg":"又r軍費<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b09dd1deb2a550508784e896e7569b0d574348c","tid":243253,"uid":76728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T13:55:21.000Z","msg":"係咁出新聞post洗底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"548f65df8a5928e76fe902ae6d379efb1eff8f24","tid":243253,"uid":25424,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T14:04:03.000Z","msg":"9up新聞<br />\nD電咪又要發電機出<br />\n你依家用既電多左，部發電機一係大D，一係開行D，咪一樣大聲左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ded1dfb06eb63ab6bff0be8af92ca7dfc8903d8","tid":243253,"uid":25916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-14T14:12:32.000Z","msg":"次次都係美國出新聞<img src=\"/assets/faces/norm